oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Photograph of Louis Robinson, of Pulaski, Tenn., the owner of "Dreaming Sybil Mille", standing with the 3 year old Grand Champion Jersey cow. The cow has on a decorated halter. He is wearing a tie and has a champion ribbon in his hand.
